snippet.title: 30 Days on Ship - New Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A new gameplay video for "30 Days on Ship" has just been released. Production is moving full steam ahead, and our community now has over 126,000 members.
Sign-ups for playtests on Steam are now open. We invite you to join us! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2800370/30_Days_on_Ship/

Developed by Klapson, Madnetic Games.
